Rating: 4
I doubled everything (more than doubled the cheese) except used 2 pounds of carrots (plus about 3 more carrots) for a large group of 15, and it was really good. Be careful not to overcook the carrots when boiling them, since they cook some more in the casserole dish. This is easy and delicious.

